WEBVTT

00:06.440 --> 00:08.576
announcer:
IN THE CRIMINAL JUSTICE SYSTEM,

00:08.609 --> 00:12.413
SEXUALLY BASED OFFENSES ARE
CONSIDERED ESPECIALLY HEINOUS.

00:12.446 --> 00:14.748
IN NEW YORK CITY,
THE DEDICATED DETECTIVES

00:14.782 --> 00:16.450
WHO INVESTIGATE
THESE VICIOUS FELONIES

00:16.484 --> 00:17.718
ARE MEMBERS OF AN ELITE SQUAD

00:17.751 --> 00:20.054
KNOWN AS
THE SPECIAL VICTIMS UNIT.

00:20.088 --> 00:22.223
THESE ARE THEIR STORIES.

00:26.660 --> 00:28.162
[pounding on door]
- LARISSA.

00:28.196 --> 00:31.199
[pounding]
LARISSA!

00:31.232 --> 00:33.801
- WHO ARE YOU?
- I'M, UH, PATRICK,

00:33.834 --> 00:35.769
LARISSA'S BOYFRIEND.
- PROVE IT.

00:35.803 --> 00:38.206
- I WALK HER HOME EVERY NIGHT.
SHE...

00:38.239 --> 00:39.673
SHE DIDN'T SHOW UP AT WORK,

00:39.707 --> 00:41.309
AND SHE'S NOT ANSWERING
HER PHONE.

00:41.342 --> 00:45.213
- WELL, SHE GAVE ME A SPARE
KEY IN CASE OF EMERGENCIES.

00:45.246 --> 00:47.615
- THANK YOU.

00:53.287 --> 00:55.389
LARISSA!

00:57.525 --> 01:00.761
OH, GOD.

01:00.794 --> 01:02.796
LARISSA, WAKE UP.

01:02.830 --> 01:06.100
LARISSA, WAKE UP!

01:06.134 --> 01:07.868
- ARRGH!

01:07.901 --> 01:09.703
GET AWAY FROM BRANDY!

01:09.737 --> 01:11.672
- AAH!

01:11.705 --> 01:13.674
[men grunting]

01:13.707 --> 01:16.410
[punches thudding,
grunting]

01:18.179 --> 01:20.248
- AAH!

01:22.783 --> 01:24.618
- ATTACKED BY A NAKED MAN
IN A MASK.

01:24.652 --> 01:27.455
- THAT'S WHAT HE SAID.
NAME'S PATRICK BINDER.

01:27.488 --> 01:29.690
SCALP LACERATION, BUT HE'S
COHERENT ENOUGH TO TALK.

01:29.723 --> 01:31.259
- OKAY, AND WHAT ABOUT
THE GIRL?

01:31.292 --> 01:33.494
- LARISSA WELSH.
STILL UNCONSCIOUS.

01:33.527 --> 01:34.795
- SHE BEATEN TOO?
- NO.

01:34.828 --> 01:37.598
AN OVERDOSE OF THE SEDATIVE
ROHYPNOL.

01:37.631 --> 01:39.833
I'M TREATING HER
WITH AN ANTIDOTE,

01:39.867 --> 01:42.470
BUT IT MAY BE A WHILE
BEFORE SHE COMES TO.

01:42.503 --> 01:45.173
I FOUND VAGINAL SCARRING,

01:45.206 --> 01:47.675
BUT NO SIGN OF SEXUAL ASSAULT
OR SEMEN.

01:47.708 --> 01:49.543
- RAPIST
DIDN'T FINISH THE JOB.

01:49.577 --> 01:51.612
- HER LUCKY DAY.

01:51.645 --> 01:53.214
WHAT'S WITH ALL THE BAND-AIDS?
- SHE PRESENTED

01:53.247 --> 01:55.716
WITH MORE THAN A DOZEN
FRESH RAZOR CUTS.

01:55.749 --> 01:57.718
- SEXUAL TORTURE?

01:57.751 --> 02:01.589
- MORE LIKE BUMBLING
WITH A GILLETTE.

02:01.622 --> 02:04.825
HER ATTACKER SHAVED HER
FROM THE NECK ON DOWN.

03:03.417 --> 03:05.286
- I SHOULD HAVE SEEN
HIS FAT ASS COMING.

03:05.319 --> 03:06.554
I COULD HAVE
TAKEN HIM EASY.

03:06.587 --> 03:08.456
- GUY IN HIS UNDERWEAR
SWINGING A TRIPOD?

03:08.489 --> 03:09.757
YOU'RE LUCKY TO BE ALIVE.

03:09.790 --> 03:11.625
- I GREW UP
WITH THREE OLDER BROTHERS.

03:11.659 --> 03:13.494
I CAN TAKE A BEATING
TO THE HEAD.

03:13.527 --> 03:15.763
- SO HOW LONG HAVE YOU
AND LARISSA BEEN DATING?

03:15.796 --> 03:17.598
- ABOUT SIX MONTHS.

03:17.631 --> 03:19.467
BUT WE'VE KNOWN EACH OTHER
FOR TWO YEARS.

03:19.500 --> 03:20.834
TOOK HER THAT LONG

03:20.868 --> 03:22.770
TO OPEN HERSELF UP
TO A RELATIONSHIP.

03:22.803 --> 03:24.772
- ANY IDEA WHY?

03:24.805 --> 03:27.241
- SHE WAS A FOSTER KID.

03:27.275 --> 03:30.911
BUT SHE'S ALWAYS BEEN
TIGHT-LIPPED ABOUT IT.

03:30.944 --> 03:34.248
WHENEVER I TRIED TO GET CLOSE,
SHE PUSHED ME AWAY.

03:34.282 --> 03:35.383
- AND HER ATTACKER.

03:35.416 --> 03:37.518
YOU EVER SEEN HIM AROUND?
- NEVER.

03:37.551 --> 03:39.387
I WOULD HAVE REMEMBERED.
FAT, SWEATY CREEP.

03:39.420 --> 03:41.689
- AND YOU DIDN'T SEE HIS FACE
'CAUSE OF THE MASK.

03:41.722 --> 03:43.424
- IF I DID,
I WOULD'VE PUNCHED IT IN.

03:43.457 --> 03:45.826
- WE'RE GONNA WANT A NURSE
TO SCRAPE YOUR NAILS,

03:45.859 --> 03:47.928
CHECK FOR HAIRS THAT THE PERP
MIGHT HAVE LEFT ON YOU

03:47.961 --> 03:49.463
DURING THE STRUGGLE.

03:49.497 --> 03:51.299
- WHATEVER IT TAKES
TO CATCH THE BASTARD.

03:51.332 --> 03:52.500
- ONE MORE THING.

03:52.533 --> 03:53.934
THE UNDERWEAR
THAT DRESSED LARISSA IN

03:53.967 --> 03:55.769
HAD THE NAME BRANDY ON IT.

03:55.803 --> 03:58.872
ANY IDEA WHO THAT IS?
- NO.

03:58.906 --> 04:00.308
EXCEPT...

04:00.341 --> 04:02.976
LARISSA TOLD ME
SHE HATES THAT NAME.

04:03.010 --> 04:05.479
- ONLY IN NEW YORK
COULD YOU HAVE NO WITNESSES

04:05.513 --> 04:06.880
TO A MASKED MAN
RUNNING DOWN THE STREET

04:06.914 --> 04:08.382
IN HIS TIGHTY-WHITIES.

04:08.416 --> 04:10.684
- NO DNA FROM PATRICK
OR LARISSA'S RAPE KITS.

04:10.718 --> 04:12.486
THE HAIR AND BLOOD
FROM THE RAZORS

04:12.520 --> 04:13.921
ONLY MATCHES LARISSA.

04:13.954 --> 04:15.823
- THEY FOUND PILLS
ALL OVER THE PLACE, DIDN'T THEY?

04:15.856 --> 04:17.391
- YEAH, THE ROOFIES
USED ON LARISSA,

04:17.425 --> 04:19.393
AND VIAGRA YOU FIGURE THE PERP
WAS USING ON HIMSELF.

04:19.427 --> 04:20.861
- IT'S A GOOD THING
PATRICK SHOWED UP.

04:20.894 --> 04:23.431
A PERP ON VIAGRA?
COULD HAVE RAPED HER FOR HOURS.

04:23.464 --> 04:24.932
- THIS WASN'T THE HUMP'S
FIRST BRANDY.

04:24.965 --> 04:26.133
- WHAT DO YOU GOT?

04:26.166 --> 04:29.370
- PERP'S M.O. MATCHES THE RAPES
OF TWO TEN-YEAR-OLD GIRLS

04:29.403 --> 04:31.572
FROM JERSEY AND CONNECTICUT
IN THE LAST YEAR.

04:31.605 --> 04:33.374
- I'VE NEVER SEEN A CASE
WHERE A RAPIST TARGETS

04:33.407 --> 04:35.676
ADULT WOMEN AND LITTLE GIRLS.

04:35.709 --> 04:37.811
- MAYBE WHY HE SHAVED LARISSA,
MAKE HER LOOK LIKE A KID.

04:37.845 --> 04:39.580
- THIS HAS TO BE OUR GUY.
BOTH GIRLS HAVE

04:39.613 --> 04:42.483
LONG, BLONDE HAIR WHICH
THE RAPIST PUT IN PIGTAILS,

04:42.516 --> 04:44.452
AND HE CALLED 'EM BOTH
BRANDY.

04:46.887 --> 04:49.423
- I DON'T KNOW WHY
HE CALLED ME THAT.

04:49.457 --> 04:51.492
MY NAME'S KELLY.

04:51.525 --> 04:53.394
- CAN YOU DESCRIBE HIM?

04:53.427 --> 04:56.464
- HE WAS GROSS.
AND FAT.

04:56.497 --> 04:59.967
AND HE MADE ME DO MY HAIR
LIKE THE GIRL IN THE PICTURE.

05:00.000 --> 05:02.002
- HE SHOWED YOU PICTURES?

05:02.035 --> 05:04.104
- OF A GIRL NAMED BRANDY.

05:04.137 --> 05:07.408
- HE WANTED YOU
TO LOOK LIKE HER?

05:07.441 --> 05:09.943
- YES. EVEN HERE.

05:09.977 --> 05:13.381
HE SAID BRANDY
HAD A BIRTHMARK.

05:13.414 --> 05:16.350
SO HE DREW ONE ON ME TOO.

05:16.384 --> 05:19.119
AND THEN HE HURT ME.

05:19.152 --> 05:22.523
- HE HURT ME REAL BAD,
BUT...

05:22.556 --> 05:24.892
I CAN'T SAY ANYTHING ELSE.

05:26.159 --> 05:29.797
- YOU KNOW, PAULA,
ANYTHING YOU CAN TELL ME...

05:29.830 --> 05:33.467
COULD STOP THIS MAN FROM HURTING
ANOTHER LITTLE GIRL.

05:33.501 --> 05:37.004
I JUST WANT YOU TO KNOW
YOU CAN TALK TO ME.

05:39.973 --> 05:42.843
- A-ARE YOU TESTING ME?

05:45.145 --> 05:47.548
- WELL, WHAT DO YOU MEAN
BY THAT?

05:47.581 --> 05:49.583
WHAT DO YOU MEAN,
TEST YOU?

05:49.617 --> 05:51.485
- HE SAID PEOPLE WOULD TEST ME

05:51.519 --> 05:53.621
TO TRY TO TRICK ME
INTO TELLING.

05:53.654 --> 05:56.156
- MM-HMM. AND IF YOU TOLD
ANYONE, HE WOULD HURT YOU.

05:56.189 --> 05:58.526
- ME AND DADDY.

05:58.559 --> 06:01.429
- HE ONLY SAID THAT
TO SCARE YOU.

06:01.462 --> 06:04.031
NOW, I CAN PROTECT YOU,
AND I WILL PROTECT YOU.

06:04.064 --> 06:06.434
BUT YOU HAVE TO...

06:06.467 --> 06:07.701
[sighs]

06:07.735 --> 06:10.438
TELL ME, YOU KNOW,
SOMETHING ABOUT HIM.

06:13.173 --> 06:15.443
- BUT...
WHAT ABOUT THE LETTER?

06:15.476 --> 06:17.144
- WHAT LETTER?

06:32.526 --> 06:34.161
WHO GAVE THAT TO YOU?

06:34.194 --> 06:36.897
- I FOUND IT UNDER MY PILLOW.

06:38.499 --> 06:41.101
THEY...PUT IT THERE.

06:43.236 --> 06:45.906
THEY CALL THEMSELVES...

06:45.939 --> 06:49.443
COVENTRY.

06:52.913 --> 06:55.516
- THE FBI HAS IDENTIFIED
THESE MARKS

06:55.549 --> 06:57.851
AS UNDERGROUND PEDOPHILE
TRADING SYMBOLS.

06:57.885 --> 07:00.521
I'VE SEEN THEM ON COINS
AND RINGS AND NECKLACES

07:00.554 --> 07:02.222
BUT NEVER USED
FOR INTIMIDATION PURPOSES.

07:02.255 --> 07:04.458
- PEDOPHILES USE THEM
TO IDENTIFY EACH OTHER.

07:04.492 --> 07:07.461
- LARGE TRIANGLE
SURROUNDING SMALLER TRIANGLES

07:07.495 --> 07:08.862
INDICATE BOY LOVERS.

07:08.896 --> 07:10.564
HEARTS WITHIN HEARTS,
GIRL LOVERS.

07:10.598 --> 07:12.700
BUTTERFLIES INDICATE
CHILD LOVERS

07:12.733 --> 07:14.502
THAT DON'T HAVE
A GENDER PREFERENCE.

07:14.535 --> 07:16.804
- SO YOU'RE SAYING OUR RAPIST
IS PART OF A RING.

07:16.837 --> 07:19.740
- WHETHER HE'S IN A RING OR NOT,
HE'S FIXATED ON LARISSA.

07:19.773 --> 07:22.743
HE MADE HER DRESS
AS A LITTLE GIRL, SHAVED HER.

07:22.776 --> 07:23.977
- HE STILL NEEDED VIAGRA
TO GET IT UP.

07:24.011 --> 07:24.912
- BECAUSE AS AN ADULT,

07:24.945 --> 07:27.180
SHE ONLY PARTIALLY
FULFILLED HIS DESIRES.

07:27.214 --> 07:29.082
- OKAY, HOW 'BOUT THE NAME
COVENTRY?

07:29.116 --> 07:31.018
I MEAN, WHO ARE THEY?
- THEY'RE THE BOGEYMAN.

07:31.051 --> 07:33.153
PEDOPHILES ONLY USE
THE NAME COVENTRY

07:33.186 --> 07:35.523
WHEN THEY WANNA SCARE
THEIR VICTIMS.

07:35.556 --> 07:39.059
THE FBI SAID THIS IS THE FIRST
FILM WHERE THE NAME WAS USED.

07:39.092 --> 07:41.595
- [distorted voice]
TAKE OFF YOUR CLOTHES, BRANDY.

07:41.629 --> 07:43.531
- MY NAME'S NOT BRANDY.
- SON OF A BITCH

07:43.564 --> 07:45.198
ALTERED HIS VOICE...
- DO IT!

07:45.232 --> 07:46.867
- SO WE COULDN'T I.D. HIM.
- OR COVENTRY WILL KILL

07:46.900 --> 07:51.505
YOUR MOMMY AND DADDY AND ALL
YOUR BROTHERS AND SISTERS.

07:51.539 --> 07:54.542
- OKAY. ALL RIGHT, MUNCH,
ENOUGH.

07:54.575 --> 07:56.810
WAIT A MINUTE. WAIT.
HOLD THAT. FREEZE THAT.

07:59.713 --> 08:03.917
LARISSA HAS THE SAME BIRTHMARK
AS THE KID IN THE FILM.

08:03.951 --> 08:06.554
SHE'S BRANDY.
- A LOT OF UNIDENTIFIED KIDS

08:06.587 --> 08:08.055
ARE PART OF
THIS COVENTRY SERIES.

08:08.088 --> 08:10.023
BUT BRANDY
WAS THE MOST POPULAR,

08:10.057 --> 08:12.526
DUE SPECIFICALLY
TO A STAR-SHAPED BIRTHMARK.

08:12.560 --> 08:14.161
- GOT SOMETHING
THAT'LL INTEREST YOU.

08:14.194 --> 08:16.263
COULDN'T PULL ANYTHING
OFF THE ACTUAL LETTER,

08:16.296 --> 08:17.130
BUT NEW IMAGING TECHNOLOGY

08:17.164 --> 08:19.232
LETS ME ZOOM IN
ON THE PERP'S FINGERTIP.

08:19.266 --> 08:21.201
Munch: YOU CAN GET
A PRINT OFF A PHOTO?

08:21.234 --> 08:24.905
- AND RUN IT FOR A MATCH.

08:24.938 --> 08:26.607
- ELDON BALOGH.

08:26.640 --> 08:28.208
HE DID TIME IN 2006

08:28.241 --> 08:30.878
FOR LEWD AND LASCIVIOUS ACTS
WITH A CHILD.

08:30.911 --> 08:33.080
- AND LIVES IN PARK SLOPE.

08:33.113 --> 08:34.081
- POLICE! SEARCH WARRANT!

08:34.114 --> 08:35.215
- NYPD!

08:35.248 --> 08:36.984
ELDON BALOGH,
SHOW YOURSELF!

08:39.587 --> 08:40.788
- CLEAR!

08:40.821 --> 08:41.955
- CLEAR!

08:41.989 --> 08:44.257
- HEY, YO, EL,
CHECK THIS OUT.

08:46.259 --> 08:49.697
IT'S VIDEO OF LARISSA
BEFORE THE BOYFRIEND ARRIVED.

08:52.232 --> 08:54.034
- LET'S CHECK THE PILLOWCASE.

08:56.303 --> 08:59.106
VIDEOS AND PICTURES.

08:59.139 --> 09:01.208
- IS THAT BRANDY?

09:03.176 --> 09:04.244
[beep]

09:04.277 --> 09:06.814
WHAT'S THAT?
[beep]

09:06.847 --> 09:09.016
[beep]

09:09.049 --> 09:10.851
[beep]

09:12.052 --> 09:15.122
HE LEFT HIS EMAIL ACCOUNT
OPEN.

09:15.155 --> 09:17.324
WHEREVER HE IS,
HE'S SENDING PHOTOS TO HIMSELF.

09:17.357 --> 09:19.927
- BRANDY. PICK 53.
OPEN THAT ONE.

09:19.960 --> 09:21.962
- IT'S LARISSA.

09:21.995 --> 09:24.097
HE'S BEEN STALKING HER
EVER SINCE THE ATTACK!

09:24.131 --> 09:25.999
- SON OF A BITCH
IS AT THE HOSPITAL.

09:26.033 --> 09:28.168
I'M GONNA CALL SECURITY.
- LIV.

09:30.303 --> 09:32.372
- [groans]
AH!

09:32.405 --> 09:34.207
- WHAT ARE YOU DOING?
- WHERE'S LARISSA WELSH?

09:34.241 --> 09:36.243
- AN ORDERLY TOOK HER FOR
TESTING 20 MINUTES AGO.

09:36.276 --> 09:38.245
- THIS GUY?
- THAT'S HIM.

09:38.278 --> 09:40.180
- AH...

09:40.213 --> 09:42.082
ANY SIGN OF HIM?
- NO, MA'AM.

09:42.115 --> 09:43.383
- LOCK THIS HOSPITAL DOWN NOW!

09:43.416 --> 09:45.653
- SECURITY, CENTRAL.
CLOSE ALL EXITS.

09:51.224 --> 09:52.960
- LIV, I'M ON MY WAY TO YOU.
WHAT'S YOUR 20?

09:52.993 --> 09:54.194
- WE'VE CLEARED
ONE THROUGH FOUR.

09:54.227 --> 09:55.929
SECURITY'S WORKING
FROM THE TOP DOWN.

09:55.963 --> 09:57.731
HEAD TO SIX AND WORK UP.

10:09.309 --> 10:11.411
[pounds twice]
- POLICE. OPEN UP.

10:11.444 --> 10:14.648
WE HAVE SOMETHING
IN ROOM 820.

10:17.317 --> 10:19.286
[zipping sound]
ZZZT.

10:19.319 --> 10:20.353
- IT'S OKAY.

10:20.387 --> 10:23.256
I WAS JUST TAKING
HER TEMPERATURE.

10:30.764 --> 10:32.265
- LET GO, EL!
EL, EL!

10:32.299 --> 10:34.935
EASY, EASY, MAN!
COME ON.

10:34.968 --> 10:36.303
MAN, COME ON, COME ON.

10:36.336 --> 10:39.139
- SON OF A BITCH
ATTACKED HER AGAIN.

10:41.008 --> 10:43.677
- [laughing]

10:50.317 --> 10:51.885
- HOW COULD THIS HAPPEN...

10:51.919 --> 10:53.353
AFTER EVERYTHING
THAT I'VE BEEN THROUGH?

10:53.386 --> 10:55.055
- LARISSA, I'M SO SORRY.

10:55.088 --> 10:57.290
- THIS HOSPITAL
LET ME GET RAPED?

10:57.324 --> 10:59.026
- PLEASE DON'T LEAVE.
LARISSA, PLEASE DON'T LEAVE.

10:59.059 --> 11:01.695
LET THE DOCTORS
KEEP AN EYE ON YOU.

11:01.729 --> 11:03.096
- WHY?

11:03.130 --> 11:05.398
'CAUSE THEY'RE DOING
SUCH A GREAT JOB?

11:05.432 --> 11:08.335
AND WHAT ABOUT YOU?
WHAT DO YOU WANT?

11:08.368 --> 11:10.137
- TO TELL YOU
THAT WE CAUGHT HIM.

11:10.170 --> 11:13.941
AND THAT HE WILL
NEVER HURT YOU AGAIN.

11:20.213 --> 11:21.815
- BEFORE HE KNOCKED ME OUT,

11:21.849 --> 11:24.451
HE SAID HE WAS GONNA
TAKE PICTURES.

11:25.786 --> 11:28.388
DID HE?

11:28.421 --> 11:30.891
- HE TOOK VIDEO.

11:30.924 --> 11:32.860
- NOT AGAIN!

11:38.198 --> 11:41.434
- THIS HAPPENED
WHEN YOU WERE A CHILD.

11:41.468 --> 11:43.871
YOU WERE BRANDY.

11:43.904 --> 11:46.774
- I ALWAYS WILL BE.

11:46.807 --> 11:48.942
- WHAT DO YOU MEAN?

11:48.976 --> 11:51.879
- SOMETIMES WHEN I'M WALKING
DOWN THE STREET

11:51.912 --> 11:54.381
OR IN THE SUBWAY,
MEN STARE AT ME.

11:54.414 --> 11:56.784
- 'CAUSE THEY RECOGNIZE YOU
FROM THE MOVIES.

11:56.817 --> 11:57.617
- YES.

11:57.650 --> 12:00.187
THEY HAVE THIS LOOK
IN THEIR EYES,

12:00.220 --> 12:02.823
YOU KNOW, PERVERTS?

12:02.856 --> 12:05.759
